    <section id="id19581228">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id21079772"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis></emphasis>The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id19613065"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Assessment Standard 1.4:</emphasis></emphasis> We know this when the learner recognises the place value of digits in:</para>
      <para id="id19824891"><emphasis effect="bold">1.4.1:</emphasis> whole numbers to at least 9-digit numbers</para>
